00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,440
just call me.

297
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,280
Wait.

298
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,520
How

299
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,520
can I trust you?

300
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:51,000
This is soul blood.

301
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,640
Sincere enough?

302
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,730
Hello there.

303
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,000
What?

304
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,100
Is there something on my face?

305
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,320
Where is the Shamo Ancestor?

306
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,040
I locked him up.

307
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,020
Don't be silly.

308
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,480
If I were really possessed,

309
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,440
your two guards would have sensed it,

310
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,160
right?

311
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:17,960
Your Majesty.

312
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,180
Let's go out first.

313
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,080
Wait.

314
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,880
Tell me a secret

315
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,410
that only the two of us know.

316
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,880
A secret?

317
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,840
You have a mole on your right butt cheek.

318
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,400
Shut up.

319
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:56,920
Daughter,

320
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:57,770
my daughter,

321
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,800
are you okay?

322
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,600
It's my fault.

323
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,010
Brother Lin.

324
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,440
Where is my brother?

325
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,370
I didn't see him.

326
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:07,660
Sister.

327
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:08,640
Brother.

328
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,640
Sister.

329
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,040
Why are these women fine?

330
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,480
They were all taken by the Soul-Catching Bell

331
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:17,080
and haven't been transformed yet.

332
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,440
Let's leave here quickly.

333
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:20,280
Staying in this place makes me uncomfortable.

334
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:20,960
Wait.

335
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,960
There's still a great demon that hasn't been eliminated.

336
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,800
Another one?

337
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,320
However, as for this demon,

338
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,960
whether it should be eliminated or not

339
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,680
depends on the decision of the Luoxian Town villagers.

340
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,640
What do you mean?

341
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,320
Let the commoners decide?

342
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,080
Yes.

343
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,130
Let them decide.

344
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,400
Am I right,

345
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:37,520
Mayor?

346
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:38,920
Or,

347
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:40,080
should I call you

348
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,480
Senior Corpse Puppet?

349
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,760
You're quite something, Young Master Lin.

350
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:52,800
How did you find out?

351
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,840
Ever since your wife awakened as a corpse demon,

352
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,400
I started to get suspicious.

353
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,200
Village head,

354
00:15:57,880 --> 00:15:58,480
could it be

355
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,530
that you are too?

356
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:00,560
No way.

357
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:01,120
The village head is...

358
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,120
Don't be nervous.

359
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:04,280
As long as you don't attack me,

360
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,520
I won't make a move.

361
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:13,960
All right.

362
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,940
Stop knocking.

363
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,440
They are done over there.

364
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,080
No.

365
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:17,800
Who are you?

366
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:18,920
Why do you care?

367
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,680
Don't delay us making money.

368
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,920
You two are fools.

369
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,320
Knocking more won't give you extra money.

370
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,320
Take a break.

371
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,400
It's so noisy. Seriously,

372
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,730
where are you from, bro?

373
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:29,760
Don't look for trouble.

374
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,600
Exactly.

375
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,720
Our boss is...

376
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,320
You two sleep here for a while.

377
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,080
This foolish girl

378
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:45,120
dared to barge into Luoxian Town all by herself.

379
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,520
She's such a worry.

380
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,680
I really didn't expect this.

381
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:54,810
I never thought it would end like this.

382
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,440
It's all fate.

383
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:58,160
The Shamo Ancestor has already left.

384
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,280
The thing you want

385
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,960
is no longer in Luoxian Town.

386
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:02,560
I figured.

387
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,240
Even if he didn't run away,

388
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,480
in my current state,

389
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:08,319
I wouldn't be able to do anything to him.

390
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:13,920
We're even.

391
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,520
Thank you, Boss Chu.

392
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:17,400
Hope we can work together again.

393
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:18,880
Work together my ass.

394
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,520
Did you three help at all?

395
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,810
Didn't I help you catch the wood demon?

396
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,810
Second Brother.

397
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,079
The wood demon was dealt with

398
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:26,680
by everyone just to save you.

399
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,160
Liu Erzhu, shut up.

400
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:29,920
Chu Xiao'er,

401
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,440
you've already made a killing.

402
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:33,000
What are you still doing here?

403
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,760
I'm waiting for you to make a move

404
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,000
and then pick up the scraps.

405
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,530
Your Highness Chu Xiao'er.

406
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:39,040
My demon core

407
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,440
isn't that easy to take.

408
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,440
Village Head.

409
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:42,720
Who exactly are you?

410
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,000
Don't you get it?

411
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:45,320
He is a corpse puppet.

412
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,520
The Lin family's corpse slaves and demons

413
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:49,080
were all refined from his demonic power.

414
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:49,920
What?

415
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:50,840
Village Head.

416
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,520
Actually,

417
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,640
the funeral procession came for you.

418
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,160
You just made your wife take your place.

419
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:55,840
Right?

420
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,360
She did it willingly.

421
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,680
She was taken by the ghost marriage and became a dark fiend.

422
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,120
I couldn't bear it.

423
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,240
So I converted her again.

424
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,520
So those bronze coffins

425
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:06,440
are specially meant to deal with him.

426
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,320
Those coffins

427
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,560
only take corpse demons,

428
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,440
not humans.

429
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,200
Xiaoying.

430
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:23,320
Brother.

431
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,960
I'm sorry.

432
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:26,800
Xiaoying.

